sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as HostStart
    participant CM as CaddyManager
    participant PM as PhpManager
    participant HM as HorizonManager
    participant OS as System Service

    User->>CLI: orbit host start service
    CLI->>CLI: Parse service argument
    
    alt service is caddy
        CLI->>CM: start
        CM->>OS: Start Caddy service
        OS-->>CM: result
        CM-->>CLI: success boolean
    else service is php-version
        CLI->>CLI: Extract version from php-X.Y
        CLI->>PM: start version
        PM->>OS: Start PHP-FPM service
        OS-->>PM: result
        PM-->>CLI: success boolean
    else service is horizon
        CLI->>HM: start
        HM->>OS: Start Horizon service
        OS-->>HM: result
        HM-->>CLI: success boolean
    else unknown service
        CLI-->>User: Error - Unknown host service
    end
    
    CLI-->>User: Started or error message
